OL,3,CHow can I see Donald Campbell's
OL,4,CBluebird K7 hydroplane in action?
OL,6,FCrowds are gathering in Coniston to
OL,7,Fwitness Donald Campbell's iconic
OL,8,FBluebird K7 returning to action on the
OL,9,Fwater.
OL,11,FThe hydroplane will complete numerous
OL,12,Fruns during a week-long festival.
OL,14,FIt is the first time the vessel has
OL,15,Freturned to the lake since the crash
OL,16,Fthat killed its record-breaking pilot
OL,17,Falmost 60 years ago.
OL,19,FWhat time will the K7 be on the water?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
