OL,3,CHow can I see Donald Campbell's
OL,4,CBluebird K7 hydroplane in action?
OL,6,FEvents are scheduled to take place
OL,7,Fbetween 10am and 5pm from the 11th of
OL,8,FMay until Sunday 17th May.
OL,10,FOrganisers say the exact timings of
OL,11,Fthe runs will depend on the weather
OL,12,Fand water conditions, but an
OL,13,Fannouncement will be make on social
OL,14,Fmedia and the public address system
OL,15,Fwhen one is scheduled to take place.
OL,17,FIt's expected to take between 30 and
OL,18,F40 minutes to bring Bluebird to the
OL,19,Fstarting point and prepare the plane
OL,20,Fbefore a run can start.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
