OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778602268
OL,3,CHow can I see Donald Campbell's
OL,4,CBluebird K7 hydroplane in action?
OL,6,FOrganisers say "safety is paramount"
OL,7,Fbut the plan is to operate runs on
OL,8,FConiston as frequently as possible
OL,9,Fthroughout the festival.
OL,11,FWhere will it run from?
OL,13,FIt will start by the Boating Centre on
OL,14,FLake Road and the course will finish
OL,15,Fopposite the Priestley Centre.
OL,17,FThe Boating Centre will have a public
OL,18,Fviewing area.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
