PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778602268
OL,3,CHow can I see Donald Campbell's
OL,4,CBluebird K7 hydroplane in action?
OL,6,FViewing of the K7 will not be possible
OL,7,Fat Sunny Bank, Brown Howe or anywhere
OL,8,Ffurther south.
OL,10,FA 'run' will involve the plane
OL,11,Ftravelling to the Priestley Centre,
OL,12,Ffollowed by a return run to the
OL,13,Fstarting point in the middle of the
OL,14,Flake.
OL,16,FHow fast will it go?
OL,18,FWeather permitting, the vessel will
OL,19,Ftake to the water for a number of
OL,20,Fpractice runs before building up to
OL,21,Fquicker speeds.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
