PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778602268
OL,3,CHow can I see Donald Campbell's
OL,4,CBluebird K7 hydroplane in action?
OL,6,FCampbell's speed record on Coniston
OL,7,Fwas 260.35mph, but for safety reasons
OL,8,Fthere will be no attempt to match such
OL,9,Fspeeds.
OL,11,FDuring the week it is expected the K7
OL,12,Fwill hit speeds of up to 150mph.
OL,14,FThe hydroplane will be piloted by Dave
OL,15,FWarby, who is an Australian world
OL,16,Fwater speed record challenger.
OL,18,FWhere can I park?
OL,20,FPeople can pay to park on site next to
OL,21,Fthe event.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
