PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778602268
OL,3,CHow can I see Donald Campbell's
OL,4,CBluebird K7 hydroplane in action?
OL,6,FParking will cost #25 per day for cars
OL,7,Fand #10 per day for motorcycles.
OL,9,FPasses can be booked in advance on the
OL,10,FBluebird Festival website and weekly
OL,11,Fpasses are also available.
OL,13,FOrganisers say the park and ride will
OL,14,Fopen when onsite parking has reached
OL,15,Fmaximum capacity.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
